title: Goodfellas - The Complete Soundtrack Collection
description:
I've always been disappointed by the soundtrack album to GOODFELLAS. Where's "Atlantis"? Where's "Jump Into The Fire?" I'm amazed they even got "Rags to Riches" on there. To that end, I've put together a collection just just about all of the music from the film.


1. Rags to Riches - Tony Bennet
2. Can't We Be Sweathearts - The Cleftones
3. Hearts of Stone - Otis Williams and the Charms
4. Sincerely - The Moonglows
5. Firenze Sogna - Giuseppe di Stefano
6. Speedo - The Cadillacs
7. Parlami d'amoreMariu - Giuseppe di Stefano

9. This World We Live In (Il cielo un una stanza) - Mina
10. Playboy - The Marvellettes

16. Life Is But a Dream - The Harptones
